ates, similar to that in the black hole information problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 16:18:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 02:59:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 12:58:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-18"}
