n the cloud-crushing time. We develop simple analytic models that\nexplain the simulated cloud destruction times in this regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 21:00:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2019 01:42:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
