y the\nmodels M1 and M3. Finally, the effect of the $N(1680)P_{11}$ narrow resonance\non the cross section of both isospin channels is explored. It is found that the\neffect is more sensitive in the $\\gamma n\\to K^0\\Lambda$ channel. In this case\nthe model M3, that fits both CLAS and MAMI data, yields a more realistic\neffect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Sep 2019 02:31:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
