mbiguous\nidentification of single barium atoms in the sensor, and permitting a positive\nidentification of the $\\beta\\beta0\\nu$ decay of Xe-136 in a gas chamber, that\ncould led to a background-free experiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Sep 2019 09:16:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 07:45:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2019 20:04:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2019 10:13:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
