 we will present the MAGIC program for\ntransient sources and how it was adapted in the current multi-wavelength and\nmulti-messenger panorama.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Sep 2019 10:00:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-09"}
